@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At KhumaloCraft Emporium, we are committed to transparency, integrity, and the protection of your rights as a valued customer. Our website policy outlines our practices regarding privacy, terms of service, and security to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for all users.
</p>

<h2>Privacy Policy:</h2>
<p>
    Your privacy is paramount to us. Our Privacy Policy details how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you interact with our website. We adhere to strict privacy standards to protect your data and ensure confidentiality. By using our website, you consent to the practices outlined in our Privacy Policy.
</p>

<h2>Terms of Service:</h2>
<p>
    By accessing or using our website, you agree to abide by our Terms of Service. These terms govern your use of our platform, including purchasing products, posting content, and interacting with other users. We encourage you to review our Terms of Service to understand your rights and obligations when using KhumaloCraft Emporium.
</p>

<h2>Security Measures:</h2>
<p>
    We prioritize the security of our platform to safeguard your personal information and ensure a secure browsing experience. Our website employs industry-standard security measures, including encryption and firewalls, to protect against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of data. We continuously monitor and update our security protocols to mitigate risks and vulnerabilities.
</p>

<h2>Cookie Policy:</h2>
<p>
    Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience and provide personalized content. Our Cookie Policy explains how we use cookies, what information they collect, and how you can manage your cookie preferences. By continuing to use our website, you consent to the use of cookies as described in our Cookie Policy.
</p>

<h2>Feedback and Contact:</h2>
<p>
    We value your feedback and encourage open communication. If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding our website policy, please don't hesitate to contact us. Your input helps us improve our services and better serve your needs.
</p>

<p>
    Thank you for choosing KhumaloCraft Emporium. We are dedicated to providing a safe, transparent, and enjoyable shopping experience for our customers.
</p>